{"tid":2206570,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"跟餓鬼爭食 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-09-17T14:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T14:20:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb0f181acef2d6f273382a25cbf9ff4805c6f2d","tid":2206570,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T14:20:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200917/BOQAGO2VFBB35LW33ZNQI5GT6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200917%2FBOQAGO2VFBB35LW33ZNQI5GT6U%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=fea7daa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200917%2FBOQAGO2VFBB35LW33ZNQI5GT6U%2F&h=31925e65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200917/BOQAGO2VFBB35LW33ZNQI5GT6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n跟餓鬼爭食 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dhGRv2h0qfXASi4Ie6AlEIwjXD8=/713x449/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UCWJ6FPBVFGB3PCVKD5JRWRMSM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdhGRv2h0qfXASi4Ie6AlEIwjXD8%3D%2F713x449%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUCWJ6FPBVFGB3PCVKD5JRWRMSM.png&h=6f72bf7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n踏入農曆七月，香港到處可見民眾路祭及燒衣紙，同時以食物作祭品，請野鬼「開餐」。農曆七月香港街頭這一獨特現象，是本港習俗。<br />\n<br />\n多年來，野鬼開餐，從來不受陽間巿民滋擾。沒想到今年遇上勁敵了！在中大政治及行政學系任職的中國助理教授李薇，看到街頭到處是野鬼的美食，竟然垂涎起來。「披星戴月」去搜刮美食，拿回家（不，應該說是搶回家，從野鬼口中搶的）炮製成三餸一湯，而且還兼顧營養全面，連飯後生果橙都有，放上網絡，沾沾自喜形容「簡單美味」。被網民不齒後更回應：「我開心關你屁事」。<br />\n<br />\n中國人一向自我，。。<br />\n。。<br />\n<br />\n餓鬼遇到這。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n網民的行動略快一步，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李薇不是初來香港，過去數年，她不曾跟餓鬼搶食，今年是特別飢餓，還是特別勇武？又或者是為了追隨中國推行的「惜食令」？真正的原因只有她自己知道。但中國人的厲害，令鬼也要寫個服字，這一點，毋庸置疑。"}]}